| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0394 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d65a678b-e95e-510e-993d-ec6e4f079c9f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
